column1: Regular traffic reports will resume Monday October 29 at 4:00 p.m.

column4: Roadway shutdown to thru traffic between Spurr Rd and Iron Works Pike until further notice.  Serious collision in the area between Berea Rd and Iron Works Pike.
Traffic from Georgetown to Lexington on US-25, detour to Iron Works Pike and I-75S.
Traffic from Lexington to Georgetown on US-25, detour to Citation Blvd to Newtown Pike to I-75N.
